summary:
- **Substantial holder change**: CAPITAL DI LIMITED increased its holding in ASARA RESOURCES LTD to 157,200,000 ordinary shares (11.42% voting power) from 150,000,000 shares (13.62%).  
- **Reason for change**:  
  - On-market purchase of 7,200,000 shares (AUD 360,000) on 25/07/25.  
  - Dilution to 11.42% due to ASARA issuing 275,294,461 new shares on 05/08/25.  

No other material information identified.
